OL,3,CTwo arrests after body found in
OL,4,Csuitcase in woodland
OL,6,FA man's body has been found inside a
OL,7,Fsuitcase in woodland in Kent, by
OL,8,Fofficers investigating a potential
OL,9,Fmurder in London.
OL,11,FAt around 10.55pm on Thursday, 9 July,
OL,12,Fpolice received a report of an
OL,13,Fincident at an address on Kingfisher
OL,14,FCourt, off Queensmere Road in
OL,15,FWandsworth.
OL,17,FNo-one was found in the property but
OL,18,Fafter carrying out a search, officers
OL,19,Fbelieved someone had come to harm at
OL,20,Fthe address and an investigation was
OL,21,Flaunched.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
