OL,3,CTwo arrests after body found in
OL,4,Csuitcase in woodland
OL,6,FOn Friday, 10 July, the Met was
OL,7,Fnotified that two men, aged 27 and 32,
OL,8,Fhad attended Medway Police Station in
OL,9,FGillingham, Kent.
OL,11,FThey were arrested on suspicion of
OL,12,Fmurder and remain in custody.
OL,14,FLater that day, officers attended a
OL,15,Fwooded area in Borstal, Kent where a
OL,16,Fman
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
