CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783878541
OL,3,CTwo arrests after body found in
OL,4,Csuitcase in woodland
OL,6,FAlthough formal identification is yet
OL,7,Fto take place, officers believe they
OL,8,Fknow the identity of the victim and
OL,9,Fhave contacted his next-of-kin, who
OL,10,Fare being supported by specialist
OL,11,Fofficers.
OL,13,FThe victim and the two men arrested
OL,14,Fwere known to each other, the force
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FA third man was also arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender,
OL,19,Fand has since been bailed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
