PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783878541
OL,3,CTwo arrests after body found in
OL,4,Csuitcase in woodland
OL,6,FDet Insp Ben Dalloway, who is leading
OL,7,Fthe investigation, said: "Our thoughts
OL,8,Fremain with the victim's family who
OL,9,Fare understandably distraught at their
OL,10,Floss. We will continue to offer them
OL,11,Fevery support."
OL,13,FHe added: "This has been a fast-moving
OL,14,Finvestigation and we are working
OL,15,Ftirelessly to establish the exact
OL,16,Fcircumstances of the incident."
